'''2015年9月博爾諾州炸彈襲擊'''，是指2015年9月20日發生在[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]][[博爾諾州|博爾諾州]]城市[[邁杜古里|邁杜古里]]和{{link-en|蒙古诺|Monguno}}的一連串[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]襲擊，懷疑由[[博科圣地|博科圣地]]發動。

== 過程 ==
2015年9月20日晚上7時左右，邁杜古里有一座[[清真寺|清真寺]]遭到炸彈襲擊，當時正值[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]的{{link-en|宵禮|Isha prayer}}時間；一名[[伊瑪目|伊瑪目]]是這場清真寺炸彈襲擊中的唯一生還者，他憶述兩名襲擊者在清真寺外面守候，而爆炸聲響起時正值[[禱告|禱告]]的中段<ref>{{cite news |title=BOKO HARAM BOMBERS KILL 54 IN BORNO |url=http://www.maritimefirstnewspaper.com/en/political/boko-haram-bombers-kill-54-in-borno/ |accessdate=2015-09-25 |agency=Maritime First Newspaper |date=2015-09-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150925152739/http://www.maritimefirstnewspaper.com/en/political/boko-haram-bombers-kill-54-in-borno/ |archivedate=2015-09-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

在相近時間，邁杜古里一個[[平交道口|平交道口]]亦發生襲擊；有生還者憶述，襲擊發生在一個[[電訊|電訊]]服務熱點，人們正在購買手機充值卡，很多人在爆炸後當場死去或受傷，不少屍體被炸得粉碎<ref>{{cite news |author1=Ndahi Marama |title=Scores feared dead as multiple explosions rock Maiduguri |url=http://www.vanguardngr.com/2015/09/scores-feared-dead-as-multiple-explosions-rock-maiduguri-2/ |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=Vanguard |date=2015-09-21 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150926030910/http://www.vanguardngr.com/2015/09/scores-feared-dead-as-multiple-explosions-rock-maiduguri-2/ |archivedate=2015-09-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

在另一宗炸彈襲擊的現場，有個大屏幕正在放映[[足球比賽|足球比賽]]，一批球迷聚集在大屏幕前觀賞賽事；爆炸後，有目擊者在襲擊現場發現四具屍體，也有很多人受傷<ref>{{cite news |title=54 die as Boko Haram hits northeastern Nigeria city – Attacks target worshippers, football fans |url=http://news.kuwaittimes.net/website/54-die-as-boko-haram-hits-northeastern-nigeria-city-attacks-target-worshippers-football-fans/ |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=Kuwait Times |date=2015-09-21 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150926032245/http://news.kuwaittimes.net/website/54-die-as-boko-haram-hits-northeastern-nigeria-city-attacks-target-worshippers-football-fans/ |archivedate=2015-09-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

另外一宗襲擊同在晚上7時發生，一名女性炸彈襲擊者在邁杜古里一所繁忙的市場內引爆炸彈<ref name=market>{{cite news |author1=Tian Shaohui (編) |title=54 killed in NE Nigeria's multiple explosion: police |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2015-09/22/c_134646156.htm |accessdate=2015-09-25 |agency=Xinhua |date=2015-09-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150925145946/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2015-09/22/c_134646156.htm |archivedate=2015-09-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>；當時，一些[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]打算購買食品，準備迎接[[古爾邦節|古爾邦節]]假期<ref>{{cite news |title=Several die in Nigeria terror attacks by Boko Haram |url=http://www.netherlandsnews.net/index.php/sid/236971233 |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=Netherlands News.Net |date=2015-09-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150926040052/http://www.netherlandsnews.net/index.php/sid/236971233 |archivedate=2015-09-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。雖然這宗爆炸案被認為是一宗[[自殺式襲擊|自殺式襲擊]]，但亦有人持相反看法，認為涉事的炸彈是被人放置在市場內；有目撃者憶述，現場有最少23具屍體和20名傷者，而爆炸現場周遭的大部分商店均被炸燬<ref>{{cite news |author1=Ujunwa Ochulo |title=Nigeria: Over 20 Killed in Market Bombing in Maiduguri Borno State |url=http://www.ngrguardiannews.com/2015/09/over-20-killed-in-market-bombing-in-maiduguri-borno-state/ |accessdate=2015-09-25 |agency=The Guardian Nigeria |date=2015-09-23 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150925160841/http://www.ngrguardiannews.com/2015/09/over-20-killed-in-market-bombing-in-maiduguri-borno-state/ |archivedate=2015-09-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

距離邁杜古里約{{convert|130|km}}的蒙古諾也發生了爆炸，當地有一所市場遭到自殺式襲擊，最少28人死亡、約55人受傷；死傷者被送到邁杜古里的醫院，但有醫院不夠空間容納他們，要求傷者轉到其他醫院接受治療<ref>{{cite news |author1=Joel Duku |title=30 traders killed, 55 injured in Borno |url=http://thenationonlineng.net/30-traders-killed-55-injured-in-borno/ |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=The Nation |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150926043208/http://thenationonlineng.net/30-traders-killed-55-injured-in-borno/ |archivedate=2015-09-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。是次襲擊共有兩枚炸彈爆炸<ref>{{cite news |title=At least 80 people killed in bomb blasts in Nigeria’s Borno state |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/537806/news/world/at-least-80-people-killed-in-bomb-blasts-in-nigeria-s-borno-state |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=GMA News Online |date=2015-09-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150926044704/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/537806/news/world/at-least-80-people-killed-in-bomb-blasts-in-nigeria-s-borno-state |archivedate=2015-09-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

截至2015年9月22日，邁杜古里的炸彈襲擊共造成最少117人死亡、70人受傷<ref>{{cite news |title=Death toll hits 117 after NE Nigeria bombings: medics |url=http://news.yahoo.com/death-toll-hits-117-ne-nigeria-bombings-medics-185008557.html |accessdate=2015-09-27 |agency=AFP |date=2015-09-22 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6bkETsIm3?url=http://news.yahoo.com/death-toll-hits-117-ne-nigeria-bombings-medics-185008557.html |archivedate=2015-09-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 責任 ==
截至2015年9月21日，沒有任何組織為是次襲擊承認責任；但是，這宗襲擊初步懷疑是由{{link-en|伊斯蘭極端主義|Islamic extremism}}組織[[博科聖地|博科聖地]]發動，該組織的武裝份子本來佔據了尼日利亞的部分領土，但這些領土被{{link-en|尼日利亞武裝力量|Nigerian Armed Forces}}在是次襲擊前收復<ref>{{cite news |author1=HARUNA UMAR |author2=JOSSY OLA |title=Nigerian Official: 54 Die in Blasts in Borno State Capital |url=http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/09/21/nigerian-official-8-dead-in-3-blasts-in-borno-state-capital |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=Associated Press |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151217092222/http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/09/21/nigerian-official-8-dead-in-3-blasts-in-borno-state-capital |archivedate=2015-12-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。博科聖地早前也曾襲擊民用設施，例如鬧市、清真寺、[[教堂|教堂]]等<ref name=noaddress>{{cite news|title=Nigeria places strict curfew in Borno after fatal bombing|accessdate=2015-09-26|agency=Daily Dispatch|date=2015-09-24}}</ref>。

== 反應 ==
[[聯合國秘書長|聯合國秘書長]][[潘基文|潘基文]]譴責博科聖地涉嫌在清真寺和其他地區發動的襲擊，又向死傷者家屬表示慰问，祝願傷者能早日康復<ref>{{cite news |title=Bomb Blast Kills 27 in Monguno as Ban Ki-moon Condemns Maiduguri Attack |url=http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/bomb-blast-kills-27-in-monguno-as-ban-ki-moon-condemns-maiduguri-attack/220969/ |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=THISDAY LIVE |date=2015-09-23 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150926113307/http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/bomb-blast-kills-27-in-monguno-as-ban-ki-moon-condemns-maiduguri-attack/220969/ |archivedate=2015-09-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。尼日利亞團體{{link-en|艾勒瓦协商政坛|Arewa Consultative Forum}}對是次襲擊表示震驚，形容襲擊卑鄙、野蠻和邪惡，是「無理地殺害無辜的靈魂」；該組織認為，博科聖地是以[[宗教戰爭|宗教戰爭]]之名殺死無辜者，沒有[[宗教|宗教]]會縱容如此殘酷野蠻的行為<ref>{{cite news |author1=Saxone Akhaine |author2=Cornelius Essen |title=ACF condemns Boko Haram killings in Borno |url=http://www.ngrguardiannews.com/2015/09/acf-condemns-boko-haram-killings-in-borno/ |accessdate=2015-09-26 |agency=The Guardian Nigeria |date=2015-09-23 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150926123805/http://www.ngrguardiannews.com/2015/09/acf-condemns-boko-haram-killings-in-borno/ |archivedate=2015-09-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

襲擊發生後，尼日利亞宣佈實施[[宵禁|宵禁]]，又禁止民眾在{{link-en|穆斯林節日|Muslim holidays}}期間駕車<ref name=noaddress/>。

